**File:** `cas-injector/src/main/java/com/oreki/cas_injector/core/GoogleSheetService.java`

**Problem:** `fetchLatestStrategy()` makes an HTTP call to the Google Sheets CSV URL every time it's called. With `computeSipPlan`, `computeOpportunisticSignals`, `computeActiveSellSignals`, and `computeExitQueue` all calling it for every API request, that's 4 external HTTP calls per page load.

